== Settings for the loading screen ==

==== "Go!" button ====
Within the [[Main Menu]] [[Settings]] menu, under the '''User Interface''' tab, there is an option to toggle a "Go!" button on load. Having this setting enabled requires the user to click the Go button before loading into the world. Disabling the setting will remove the Go button, causing you to automatically join when the download is completed.

==== Preloading worlds ====
When browsing a world's page from within the VRChat client, an Action that can be clicked is '''Preload World'''. By preloading a world before joining, most of the loading screen can be skipped.

