** Erick McNerney has several official remixes of Passing Through on [https://www.youtube.com/@ErickMcNerney/videos his YouTube channel].
* Before 2018, the loading screen was an outer space skybox that played "[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IrzaXcOGYbM Partially Offline]", by Andrea Baroni<ref>[https://andreabaroni.com/ Andrea Baroni's website] at ''andreabaroni.com''; retrieved May 26, 2025</ref>.
** This particular loading screen is re-created in the [https://vrchat.com/home/world/wrld_bfb3e4ad-0952-48f6-82c8-23b66c340f4a/ VRChat Home - 10 Years] world.
** Partially Offline can also be heard in the [[VRChat Home]] music player.
* It might be speculated that the loading screen is a world called [https://vrchat.com/home/world/inbetween/info The In-Between].

